		}
		{
			dependencies: ["7A07000000000103"]
			description: [
				"&8[ FINAL ENTRY — RECOVERED AT HS-LGTFO SITE ]&r"
				""
				"&7I found what remained of them. The mission was not a failure. That is the part no one prepared me for.&r"
				""
				"&8It worked. They escaped.&r"
				""
				"&8And it did not matter. There was nowhere untouched. Earth was not the battlefield — it was only the first place they noticed the war.&r"
				""
				"&7\"The Old Civilisation was not destroyed.\"&r"
				"&7\"It was corrected.\"&r"
				""
				"&8Humanity's greatest achievement was discovering the universe.&r"
				"&8Humanity's greatest mistake was assuming the universe wanted to be discovered.&r"
				""
				"&8The question was never whether we can escape. It is what follows if we do.&r"
			]
			hide: true
			hide_dependency_lines: true
